cs.MM, cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.IT, cs.NI

The paper deals with multiview streaming and navigation, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) techniques. The proposed method involves coding and compression, which falls under information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses rate-distortion gain, which is a common metric in multimedia (cs.MM) research. Finally, the paper involves transmission delay, which is a concern in networked systems (cs.NI).
